queries.sql: SELECT `staff_profiles`.*, `u`.`username` as `user_username`, `u`.`email` as `user_email`, `u`.`status` as `user_status`, `ur`.`name` as `user_role_name`, `sr`.`name` as `staff_role_name`, `sd`.`name` as `department_name`, `ss`.`name` as `specialization_name` FROM `staff_profiles` LEFT JOIN `users` `u` ON `u`.`id` = `staff_profiles`.`user_id` LEFT JOIN `roles` `ur` ON `ur`.`id` = `u`.`role_id` LEFT JOIN `roles` `sr` ON `sr`.`id` = `staff_profiles`.`role_id` LEFT JOIN `staff_departments` `sd` ON `sd`.`id` = `staff_profiles`.`department_id` LEFT JOIN `staff_specializations` `ss` ON `ss`.`id` = `staff_profiles`.`specialization_id` ORDER BY `staff_profiles`.`last_name` ASC, `staff_profiles`.`first_name` ASC
